<view class="page"><view class="topbar">校园感谢墙<text class="en">THANKS WALL</text></view><view class="wall-note">只展示通过检查的感谢文字和隐藏后的拾卡者姓名，不显示学号或联系方式。</view><view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="neo-card">正在读取感谢…</view><view wx:elif="{{items.length === 0}}" class="neo-card">还没有公开感谢，完成真实归还后可留下第一条。</view><view wx:for="{{items}}" wx:key="id" class="thanks-card"><image src="/assets/icons/favorite.png" mode="aspectFit" /><view><view class="thanks-text">“{{item.text}}”</view><view class="thanks-meta">感谢 {{item.maskedFinderName}} · <text class="number">{{item.createdAt}}</text></view></view></view></view>
